paragraphs.text:
run(sql="

with m as(
    select TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(ag.orderDate/1000)) as date, count(distinct ag.subOrderId) as msite_orders 
    from `all(saleOrder)` so join `all(agCmDump)` ag on ag.orderId=so.orderId 
    where DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE(),TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(ag.orderDate/1000))) BETWEEN 1 AND 70 and (so.deviceType='WAP' or so.deviceType='Web') 
    group by ag.orderDate 
    order by ag.orderDate
),
o as(
    select TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(orderDate/1000)) as date, count(distinct subOrderId) as orders
    from `all(agCmDump)` 
    where DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE(),TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(orderDate/1000))) BETWEEN 1 AND 70
    group by orderDate
    order by orderDate
)
    select m.date, m.msite_orders, o.orders, m.msite_orders/o.orders*100 as percent from m join o on o.date=m.date order by m.date 
    
",1000)
